column5: ANIX WOW no one is selling this stock Only 664 shares sold far today Looks like we all think this is going to be a MONSTER winner in the fight against cancer

ANIX if new data coming then it looks like either the laboratory has established certain performance characteristics relating to analytical validity of the testing or they will have fully finished the CLIA testing prior to the conference which would mean they are still on track for commercial release in Q3 both scenarios are good news or is there a third scenario
